<title>USA: SS&amp;C Technologies names Stoner president.</title>
<headline>SS&amp;C Technologies names Stoner president.</headline>
<dateline>BLOOMFIELD, Conn. 1997-04-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>SS&amp;C Technologies Inc said on Tuesday it named David Stoner as president and chief operating officer.</p>
<p>William Stone, the chairman and chief executive, had previously also served as president.</p>
<p>Stoner joins SS&amp;C from Dodge Group Inc, where he was president and chief operating officer.</p>
<p>SS&amp;C provides client/server-based software products and related services.</p>
